{"tid":731531,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Sunrise 與《悍戰太平洋》公司合拍 荷李活真人版機動戰士","createTime":"2018-07-06T09:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T09:51:03.000Z","uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e327701a7a39f9a85b0cdcff10d526652b5653a","tid":731531,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"美國洛杉磯正在舉行的「Anime Expo 2018」活動，剛宣佈了日本經典科幻機械人動畫《機動戰士》會由荷李活拍真人版電影的消息，令在場動畫迷非常興奮。<br />\n<br />\n目前於美國洛杉磯所舉辦的「Anime Expo 2018」活動中，日本動畫製作公司Sunrise 與過去推出過《悍戰太平洋》、《哥斯拉》等作品的Legendary Pictures, Inc.聯合公布，他們會合作拍攝日本人氣科幻動畫《機動戰士》真人版電影的消息，只見的Legendary Pictures首發的片段中，附加一段《機動戰士》動畫初代在宇宙世紀的背景描述，讓人好奇是否在暗指真人版電影的時間設定。<br />\n<br />\n《機動戰士》自 1979 年推出至今，已推出許多電視、電影以及相關的多媒體的動畫作品，在全球皆有一定的人氣，而該系列也即將在 2019 年迎來作品的 40 周年，明年是《機動戰士》全系列而言將是一個很重要的年份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lUTcoS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lUTcoS&d=tIRv%2FMGLmht8M4%2Fqae7Cxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b8802134\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lUTcoS</a>"},{"pid":"323a3cce6358441640f61c2e8ae4b458896266b8","tid":731531,"uid":60341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"景甜做邊個"},{"pid":"b68a6e3ab9897922f2706d06d3bd9ffb1e99282f","tid":731531,"uid":60271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"323a3cce6358441640f61c2e8ae4b458896266b8","tid":731531,"uid":60341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"景甜做邊個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"做高達"},{"pid":"6dd55d1b78ffdd995ca86dda5f2463909c0563b0","tid":731531,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b68a6e3ab9897922f2706d06d3bd9ffb1e99282f","tid":731531,"uid":60271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"323a3cce6358441640f61c2e8ae4b458896266b8","tid":731531,"uid":60341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"景甜做邊個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:12:1